Package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.annotation.registration

package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.annotation.registration
Annotations to register objects from public static finalfields of classes to the LibX registration system. In order to use this, your mod must extend ModXRegistration.
  • Annotation Interfaces Summary
    Annotation Interface
    Description
    NoReg
    Exclude a field from automatic registration.
    RegisterClass
    Can be applied to a class to register all public static final fields to a ModXRegistration.
    RegName
    Set a custom name for automatic registration.
